videos.headline: Spartans take intentional safety
videos.description: Backed up at its own one-yard line, Michigan State sends the snap through the end zone to give Ohio State 2 points.

videos.headline: Buckeyes recover Spartans' fumble for TD
videos.description: Ohio State's defense recovers Michigan State's fumble in the end zone to extend its lead to 16-6.
